	GAMECARD~
		Math Clicker;
		Practice your math skills and satisfy your urge to play idle games with this fun combo of both.
		 This HTML5 game requires a keyboard to play.;
		Instructions: Type the correct answer to the math problem that appears on the screen. Click to buy upgrades that will help you solve harder problems.;
		svg/game_icons/math-clicker.svg;
		games/math-clicker/math-clicker.html;
